map ming visiting professorship map ming visiting professorship for energy and the environment about recipients to apply endowment the map ming visiting professorship for energy and the environment was established by mineral acquisition partners inc map www maproyalty com and michael and diane ming this endowment provides stanford the opportunity to invite a leading senior scholar in a selected field of energy and environment every year the scholar is in residence for three to six months and interacts with faculty and students in areas related to the science technology and or management of energy in order to enhance opportunities for interaction the scholar offers a course or an extended lecture series
